Additional details

Uigos - natural life, natural light    this uigos n30 is a light-sensing night light which emanates a soft, white glow automatically at night or in low light conditions. Ideal for indoor places like bedroom, children's room, kitchen, hallways, stairways, closets etc.   No need to push any buttons or flip a switch, just set the lighting mode and auto illuminate your living space. Wireless and portable, our led light draws minimal power (0.5w ). It is safe for use at home and around children.     Specification: - Input voltage: Ac 110-220v-power consumption: 0.5w-light color: White-lifespan: 50000 hours- dimension: 2.56 x 2.56 x 1.1in/6.5 x 6.5 x 2.8cm    -net weight: 1.4oz/40g, package: 6pcs/pack, package contents: - 6 x night light. Allows you to get up at night, get some water, use the restroom and return to bed without turning on any main lights. You don't have to worry about turning the lights on and off around the house in the morning and evening. The smart sensor does it for you.

      My house gets very dark at night and these were the perfect solution! I have one in the bathroom, one in the living room, and one in the kitchen for when I get up during the night or just whenever its dark out. They are very functional and easy to use as it just plugs into the wall. They give off the perfect amount of light to where you can see where you're walking during the night but aren't too blinding or peak through the cracks of the bedroom door. These lights can sense when the room is getting darker and automatically turn on and vice versa when it is light. These are also the perfect size to where they don't take up the whole outlet. They are very sturdy and seem like they will last awhile. No problems thus far and glad they come in a 6 pack for when I need more or find other places to put them!
